parameters:
The security key? I have it. I don't mind giving it to
you... but could you do me a small favor first?

I was playing with my dog in the 3F garden, but there are so
many guards around I can't go look for it. Could you bring
it back for me?
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
Oh, is that so... Then I won't give you the key.
Please look for the dog in the 3F garden and bring it here.

You brought them here! I'm saved, thank you. Please accept
this as a token of my gratitude.
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
Now, let's conduct plenty of experiments-.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]Eh... by experiments, could it possibly mean...

Yes, I can't concentrate on my experiments unless this
little one is beside me.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[1]Oh, that's a relief. I thought for a moment you were going
to experiment on that child...

Of course not, I wouldn't do such a thing. My experimental
partners are only young and energetic men.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]Having a puppy beside you while experimenting with young
men... I wonder what that entails...
It seems there are no traps in this area.
